Author: Oracle Version: 11.1 Last update: May-2008
Description: - Integration Knowledge Module. - Integrates data from a Netezza staging area to a file using external tables in truncate / insert (append) mode. - the BASE_TABLE option enables to specify the name of a table that will be used as a template for the external table.
Restrictions: - When using this module with a journalized source table, data are automatically filtered to not include source deletions
Change History: May-2008 - Update of description - Updated to odiRef - 5995092 fixed - "Create external table": 7011069 fixed
Automatically attempts to insert data into the Target Datastore of the Interface
Commit all data inserted in the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to truncate the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to delete all the rows of the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to create the target table

It this option is empty, the external table will be created with the structure of the interface target table. If a table name is specified, the structure of this table will be used to create the external table.

insert into ext_<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_NAME")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ", ", "", "(INS and REW)")%> ) select <%=odiRef.getPop("DISTINCT_ROWS")%> <%=odiRef.getColList("", "\t[EXPRESSION]", ",\n\t", "", "(INS and REW)")%> from <%=odiRef.getFrom()%> where <% if (odiRef.getPop("HAS_JRN").equals("0")) { %> (1=1) <%} else {%> not (JRN_FLAG = 'D') <% } %> <%=odiRef.getJoin()%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter() %> <%=odiRef.getGrpBy()%> <%=odiRef.getHaving()%>

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","JRN_NAME","A")%> where JRN_CONSUMED = '1' <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

create external table ext_<%=odiRef.getTargetTable( "TABLE_NAME")%> <% if (!"".equals(odiRef.getOption( "BASE_TABLE"))) { %> SAMEAS <%=odiRef.getOption("BASE_TABLE")%> <% } else { %> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "\t[COL_NAME]\t[SOURCE_CRE_DT] ", ",\n", "", "")%> ) <% } %> USING (DATAOBJECT('<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("WORK_SCHEMA")%>/<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("RES_NAME")%>') )

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> update <%=odiRef.getTable( "L" , "JRN_NAME" , "A" )%> set JRN_CONSUMED = '1' where (1=1) <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>
